title: New Qantas lounge in Perth is open for business
text:
Topix › Pacific Travel › New Qantas lounge in Perth is open fo... New Qantas lounge in Perth is open for business 26 min ago Read more: Sydney Morning Herald 
Qantas has opened a new domestic business lounge in Perth, complete with an Italian pizza bar, a wine bar, a 'make your own juice' station, a 'plate of the day' and a cocktail hour, as it battles against Virgin Australia to attract passengers to and from the West Australian capital amid the downturn in the resources sector. Perth now joins Sydney, Canberra, Brisbane and Melbourne as the ports where Qantas operates a business lounge separate from the Qantas Club lounge.
